response.overview: Follow Rae McDonald’s journey to compete in the national and world wrestling stage. Along the way, he’ll tell stories of his past triumphs and losses during his career, all while training for the US Open and World Wrestling Championship. Armed with his faith and support from his friends in the wrestling community, Rae will face his biggest challenge yet.
response.tagline: The Story Of World Champion Rae McDonald
response.title: Rae Rae
